{"tid":2435371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"袁國勇自行接種復必泰疫苗　稱不適合參與噴鼻疫苗臨床測試","createTime":"2021-03-06T07:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T10:23:41.000Z","uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"6c30aebfbb45259d47484a0a2b4f80cd7c72a2f0","tid":2435371,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:46:31.000Z","msg":"港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇，下午到上環中山紀念公園體育館社區疫苗接種中心，自行接種BioNTech(復必泰)新冠疫苗。他早前曾稱，會接種港大正研發的噴鼻式新冠疫苗，但今日指，接獲瑪麗醫院臨床藥物試驗中心通知，指他已經64歲，超過了60歲的一期臨床測試年齡限制，無法參與。袁國勇解釋說，無論科興疫苗，抑或復必泰疫苗，臨床數據都顯示是安全，考<span class=\"red\">慮自己本身無長期病患、腦部和心臟無血管閉塞，而且他時常會接觸到病人，要在實驗室面對新冠病毒，間中亦要巡視酒店、商場或食肆等疫區，因此決定採用副作用「較猛」、能產生較高抗體水平的復必泰疫苗，相信保護作用會大一些。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n袁國勇強調，在接種疫苗方面，無人向他施壓。他擔心接種率會受再有港人接種疫苗後死亡影響，希望為自己接種疫苗，能夠做示範榜樣。他指，打疫苗有如戴口罩，如果很少人接種，對控制疫情幫助不大；但如超過七、八成人接種，疫情就可以控制下來。"},{"pid":"9a6b16ac23a9248c666664039bd97a8f769411e8","tid":2435371,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:47:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381854\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2381854&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=b233838f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381854</a>"},{"pid":"0e47274fc8f79cf97f5330f8529041acfbbbeae3","tid":2435371,"uid":10905,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:54:32.000Z","msg":"他擔心接種率會受再有港人接種疫苗後死亡影響，希望為自己接種疫苗，能夠做示範榜樣<br />\n<br />\n有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支針見你打左就唔會再死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7375189222ec7e4dfa33fb76fcd4bf0d7b5b0ba6","tid":2435371,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T09:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d6e1c95c44d016664d7aa96f1d869d0aded034","tid":2435371,"uid":47614,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T09:55:33.000Z","msg":"自己插鼻胃喉先出聲啦<br />\n<br />\n自己打針有咩大不了"},{"pid":"38997e0b3048bf07d298e387e467b1381e340e0c","tid":2435371,"uid":297997,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T10:15:50.000Z","msg":"<em>因此決定採用副作用「較猛」</em><br />\n<br />\n維穩到一個點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9161f9256257bc876d93c3ba70c33348198be6","tid":2435371,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T10:25:57.000Z","msg":"彈出彈入"},{"pid":"994c1d240bc86408743cb14c05bc50c027878d3d","tid":2435371,"uid":350170,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T10:47:30.000Z","msg":"疫苗一針，國勇對醫生說：「我來打！」醫生看著他，他居然笑了︰「沒有嘗試過的人生，我都想嘗試一下。」"},{"pid":"7ff4b87297162d3aca999ae4b5b5ec92c244e7cb","tid":2435371,"uid":103207,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T10:51:02.000Z","msg":"講左一堆廢話，都係唔肯打科興"},{"pid":"bb116e4d8c0a105fb8243ec981bbc23e9d97ca3d","tid":2435371,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T10:52:03.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦袁狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/d